title: File Tab
text: File > Open should only be used to open existing spreadsheets, and a new spreadsheet cannot be created through opening an existing file.

title: Importing Data
text: There are a couple of different options when importing data, including importing the data into specific cells.

title: Creating a New Spreadsheet
text: It is not necessary to create a new spreadsheet when importing data, as the data can be imported to the user's current spreadsheet environment.

title: Data Types
text: It is valid to import data with multiple file types, so long as they are compatible with being numeral or textual data.
